T02TD3731E:65b-1: mah'a r'a dza bi r'upa k'a ya karma kalpa s'a dha nam /
T02TD3731E:65b-3: rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras gyi las brtag pa'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD3731E:65b-4: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3731E:65b-5: thugs gtso phyag na rdo rje yis //
T02TD3731E:65b-6: dngos su lung bstan byin brlabs pa'i //
T02TD3731E:65b-7: spyod mdzad chos gyi rdo rjes ni //
T02TD3731E:65b-8: grags 'dzin la sogs pha rol te //
T02TD3731E:65b-9: cho gas bsad sogs las rnams ni //
T02TD3731E:65b-10: bla ma brgyud pa las byung ba'i //
T02TD3731E:65b-11: gnod sbyin rgyal po gtsor gyur pa'i //
T02TD3731E:65b-12: stong phrag brgyad dang gnyis lhag pa'i //
T02TD3731E:65b-13: de sgrub cho ga bshad par bya //
T02TD3731E:65b-14: dpal ldan khro rgyal rdo rje can //
T02TD3731E:65b-16: lha tshogs gdug ba gzhom pa'i phyir //
T02TD3731E:65b-17: dang por cho ga la 'jug bya //
T02TD3731E:65b-18: ske tshe nyungs kar dug sna tshogs //
T02TD3731E:65b-19: bong bu'i chu dang spangs sogs dang //
T02TD3731E:65b-20: tsha dang gdug pa'i tsher spangs chus //
T02TD3731E:65b-21: h'um brjod sa gzhi legs par byug / kho ra tsher ma can gyi shing //
T02TD3731E:65b-22: nam phyed byang bltas me tog blang //
T02TD3731E:65b-23: tshom bu dgur ni legs par dgod //
T02TD3731E:65b-24: khrus byas bsrung ba bdun byas la //
T02TD3731E:65b-25: sems dpa'i skyil krung bde stan la //
T02TD3731E:65b-26: byang du mngon phyogs 'jug par bya //
T02TD3731E:65b-27: de nyid rigs kyi me tog dang //
T02TD3731E:65b-28: sna tshogs dug phye mi rus phye //
T02TD3731E:65b-29: legs par sbyar ba'i de bzhin spos //
T02TD3731E:65b-30: mi rkang las byung mar med dang //
T02TD3731E:65b-31: s'a lu dmar po sha lnga sogs //
T02TD3731E:65b-32: gcig tu byas pa'i lha bshos dang //
T02TD3731E:65b-33: mi dang bong bu'i dri chu dang //
T02TD3731E:65b-34: rma bya'i sgo dang ku shar bcas //
T02TD3731E:65b-35: bsang gtor dri yi chu dang ldan //
T02TD3731E:65b-36: sngags rgyal bcu gsum pa bzlas bya //
T02TD3731E:65b-37: phyogs mtshams kun du bsang gtor bya //
T02TD3731E:65b-38: de nas bdag nyid rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD3731E:66a-1: bkrus nas brtsams sgrub thabs gzhung //
T02TD3731E:66a-2: bdag nyid cho ga rdzogs byas la //
T02TD3731E:66a-3: yi ge bcu gsum bzlas pa ni //
T02TD3731E:66a-4: 'bum phrag gcig tu bzlas byas la //
T02TD3731E:66a-5: snying gar yi ge bsams pa las //
T02TD3731E:66a-7: gnod sbyin bye ba 'bum gyi gtso ;
T02TD3731E:66a-8: / klu chen brgyad kyis bskor ba yi //
T02TD3731E:66a-9: rnam thos rgyal po spyan drangs te //
T02TD3731E:66a-10: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor steng du ni //
T02TD3731E:66a-11: rim pas legs par bzhugs par bsam //
T02TD3731E:66a-12: de la bsang gtor nas brtsams te //
T02TD3731E:66a-13: gong gi mchod pa'i rim pa yis //
T02TD3731E:66a-14: yi ge gsum dang ldan pa rnams //
T02TD3731E:66a-15: rgyal po 'khor bcas legs par mchod //
T02TD3731E:66a-16: aom aa mri ta kunda li ha na ha na h'um phat /
T02TD3731E:66a-17: de la mchod pa'i yi ge ni //
T02TD3731E:66a-18: so sor legs par sbyar te dbul //
T02TD3731E:66a-19: spyi gtsug lkog ma snying ga yi //
T02TD3731E:66a-20: yi ge gsum gyi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD3731E:66a-21: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
T02TD3731E:66a-22: 'od zhu sa bon rang bzhin bya //
T02TD3731E:66a-23: de la rang sngags bskor ba dmigs //
T02TD3731E:66a-24: 'od kyis gdug pa bcom byas te //
T02TD3731E:66a-25: slar bsdu h'um sogs la thim nas //
T02TD3731E:66a-26: rgyal chen 'khor bcas yongs su rdzogs //
T02TD3731E:66a-27: klu rnams yi ge phu:las bskyed //
T02TD3731E:66a-28: de nyid rgyal po chen po ste //
T02TD3731E:66a-29: sku mdog sngon po gzi brjid can //
T02TD3731E:66a-30: zhal gcig pa la phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD3731E:66a-31: khro gnyer mche ba cung zhig gtsigs //
T02TD3731E:66a-32: cod pa na sbrul mgo chun 'phyang lding //
T02TD3731E:66a-33: phrag gong g-yas g-yon nyi zlas mtshan //
T02TD3731E:66a-34: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid can //
T02TD3731E:66a-35: seng ge la sogs 'jigs pas mtshan //
T02TD3731E:66a-36: sku las nam mkha' gang bar 'phro //
T02TD3731E:66a-37: g-yas na rdo rjes rab mtshan pa'i ;
T02TD3731E:66a-38: / dbyug pa ba dan bcas pa 'dzin //
T02TD3731E:66a-39: g-yon pa phyag na sku gdung 'dzin //
T02TD3731E:66a-40: klu rnams gdug pa'i rang lus 'chang //
T02TD3731E:66a-41: gnod sbyin srin po'i gzugs rnams ni //
T02TD3731E:66a-42: nam mkha'i sprin tshogs bzhin du bsam //
T02TD3731E:66a-43: thugs ka'i sa bon las 'phros pa'i //
T02TD3731E:66a-44: 'od kyis rgyal po rnam thos sras ;
T02TD3731E:66a-45: /'khor dang bcas pa bkug nas ni //
T02TD3731E:66a-46: mdun gnas dkyil 'khor dag la bstim //
T02TD3731E:66a-47: de nas bsang gtor nas brtsams te //
T02TD3731E:66a-48: gong gi sngags kyis mchod pa dbul //
T02TD3731E:66a-49: gong gi gtor ma'i cho ga bzhin //
T02TD3731E:66a-50: legs par byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-0: aom badzra bi ru r'a ga / ku be @66b ra a'a tam ka / ma h'a yaksha r'a dza /
T02TD3731E:66b-1: aashda n'a ga bi ra bee ka sarba yaksha pa ci b'a ra ai dam ba lim grim h'a ntu /
T02TD3731E:66b-3: ma ma siddhim phra ya tstsha /
T02TD3731E:66b-5: s'a dha aa mu ka m'a ra ya h'um phat s'a h'a /
T02TD3731E:66b-6: yi ge bco lnga sngags la ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-7: btags te gtor ma dbul bar bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-8: de nas bdag nyid bsrung bar bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-9: gser la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams la //
T02TD3731E:66b-10: h'um ngam khrom gyi phyi rol du //
T02TD3731E:66b-11: yi ge bcu gsum bskor bar bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-12: nyungs kar dang bcas spyi bor gzhag / gla rtsi ba yi rnam lnga la //
T02TD3731E:66b-13: gos sngon can gyi sngags bzlas te //
T02TD3731E:66b-14: mgo lus khyab par byugs la bsrung //
T02TD3731E:66b-15: de nas rten 'brel sngags kyis ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-16: lus la go cha dgod par bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-17: spyi bo klog ma snying ga ru //
T02TD3731E:66b-18: kha dog gsum ldan yi ge bsam //
T02TD3731E:66b-19: so sor sngags kyis bskor bar bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-20: thugs kar zla ba la gnas h'um //
T02TD3731E:66b-21: de la sngags kyis yongs bskor te //
T02TD3731E:66b-22: lce la rdo rje sbu gu bsam //
T02TD3731E:66b-23: spro bsdu'i sngags gyi bzlas pa ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-24: rgyal po'i thugs kar dmigs la bzlas //
T02TD3731E:66b-25: dal min myur ba ma yin dang //
T02TD3731E:66b-26: gsal min mi gsal ma yin par //
T02TD3731E:66b-27: rtse gcig sems kyis bzlas bar bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-28: aom n'i l'a mab ra dha ra badzra p'a ni mah'a yaksha r'a dza ku be ra bi ru r'a ga siddhi mme phra ya tstsha h'um h'um h'um phat /
T02TD3731E:66b-29: 'di brjod bsnyen pa 'bum phrag gcig / rdzogs nas rmi ltas 'byung ba ste //
T02TD3731E:66b-30: chu bo skams dang sbrul mthong ngam //
T02TD3731E:66b-31: sbra khyim nags la me mched mthong //
T02TD3731E:66b-32: sog po srin pos bskor ba yi //
T02TD3731E:66b-33: dbus na gnas pa mthong ba'am //
T02TD3731E:66b-34: seng ge la sogs gcan gzan tshogs //
T02TD3731E:66b-35: mdun 'dus gus par mthong ba na ;
T02TD3731E:66b-36: / de nas las sbyor brtsam par bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-37: gnas gsum thig le byas nas su //
T02TD3731E:66b-38: gong gi bsrung ba'i chog rnams //
T02TD3731E:66b-39: bsrungs te byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD3731E:66b-40: dur khrod rdo leb thog tu ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-41: sna tshogs rdo rje bris byas la //
T02TD3731E:66b-42: steng du dug dang lan tshva dang //
T02TD3731E:66b-43: khrag dang chu 'gram gnyis kyi sa ;
T02TD3731E:66b-44: / rkang rjes sa la sogs pa la //
T02TD3731E:66b-45: bsgrub bya'i gzugs sam gdug pa'i gzugs //
T02TD3731E:66b-46: rang gzugs mtshan nyid ldan par bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-47: dgug dang bcing ba la sogs pa'i //
T02TD3731E:66b-48: bsad pa'i cho ga byas nas ni //
T02TD3731E:66b-49: de la sbyin sreg brtsams par bya //
T02TD3731E:66b-50: me thab gru gsum thab khung la //
T02TD3731E:67a-1: la khru re'i tshad yod de //
T02TD3731E:67a-2: zabs su khru phyed la sogs la //
T02TD3731E:67a-3: sbyin sreg cho gar gsungs pa bzhin //
T02TD3731E:67a-4: thab kyi mtshan nyid shes par bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-5: de yi dbus su mchod rten ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-6: dur khrod tshon ni nag pos bris //
T02TD3731E:67a-7: de dbus rdo rje dbyug pa ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-8: ba dan rtse ldas mtshan par bya//
T02TD3731E:67a-9: de yi phyi rol phyogs mtshams su //
T02TD3731E:67a-10: kha dog nag po sbrul brgyad bri //
T02TD3731E:67a-11: gzhan dag dkyil 'khor phyag mtshan rnams //
T02TD3731E:67a-12: sbyin sreg cho gar shes par bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-13: tsher ma dug shing khru gang la //
T02TD3731E:67a-14: dbus su zur gsum brtsig bya ste //
T02TD3731E:67a-15: mi skra'i skud pas bcing bya yis //
T02TD3731E:67a-16: tsher ma khru gang dbus su gzhag / de nas mngon spyod rdzas rnams gzhag / sreg rdzas lingga gnyis su bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-17: dug dang khrag dang ske tshe dang //
T02TD3731E:67a-19: rkang rjes sa dang da du ra //
T02TD3731E:67a-20: bra 'o sran ma mi rus phye //
T02TD3731E:67a-21: byang du mgo bstan shi ba'i skras //
T02TD3731E:67a-22: kun la bsreg pa byas nas ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-23: dug shing tsher ma sor brgyad la //
T02TD3731E:67a-24: khrag dang dug chus sbags pa yi //
T02TD3731E:67a-25: de yi yam shing dbul bar bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-26: rus phye la sogs mchod pa rnams //
T02TD3731E:67a-27: gong du gsungs pa bzhin du bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-28: de nas me ni sbar bya ste //
T02TD3731E:67a-29: dbus su rgyal po chen po ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-30: klu dang gnod sbyin tshogs bskor ba'i //
T02TD3731E:67a-31: thams cad rdzogs par bsam par bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-32: rang bzhin rgyal po bkug la bstim //
T02TD3731E:67a-33: sku stod khva dang 'ug pa dang //
T02TD3731E:67a-34: gcan gzan 'jigs tshogs spro bar bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-35: rked bar gnod sbyin 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD3731E:67a-36: mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa spro //
T02TD3731E:67a-37: sku smad seng ge la sogs pa //
T02TD3731E:67a-38: gcan gzan 'jigs pa'i tshogs su spro //
T02TD3731E:67a-39: de dag gzugs kyis bsgrub bya dang //
T02TD3731E:67a-40: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams bkug byas te //
T02TD3731E:67a-41: gong gi linggar bstim pa dang //
T02TD3731E:67a-42: nam mkha' dum bur gtubs nas ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-43: gnod sbyin rgyal po'i zhal du dbul //
T02TD3731E:67a-44: dug dang khrag la sogs pa ni //
T02TD3731E:67a-45: bdun nam nyi shu rtsa gcig bar //
T02TD3731E:67a-46: gong gi rdzas rnams dbul bar bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-47: aom badzra bi ru'i ra ka ku be ra ma h'a yaksha r'a dza /
T02TD3731E:67a-48: che ge mo aa na la ha na sarba du sht'a na /
T02TD3731E:67a-49: sarba bha smi ku ru che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat /
T02TD3731E:67a-50: des ni sbyin sreg dbul bar bya //
T02TD3731E:67a-51: gnod sbyin rgyal po'i phyag rgya yis //
T02TD3731E:67b-0: stong phrag gcig tu bsreg @67b par bya'o //
T02TD3731E:67b-1: thal ba lan tshva ske tshe dang //
T02TD3731E:67b-2: dug dang khrag gis sbrus nas ni //
T02TD3731E:67b-3: bsgrub bya'i gzugs ni khru gang tshad //
T02TD3731E:67b-4: legs par byas pa'i snying ga ru //
T02TD3731E:67b-5: 'khor lo rtsi bas ni bcu gnyis pa //
T02TD3731E:67b-6: 'khor lo de yi lte bar ni //
T02TD3731E:67b-7: h'um gnyis bar du ming bkod de //
T02TD3731E:67b-8: de li lte ba'i mu khyud la //
T02TD3731E:67b-9: yi ge bcu gsum dgod par bya //
T02TD3731E:67b-10: phyi rol rtsi bas ni bcu gnyis la //
T02TD3731E:67b-11: badzra bi r'u ra ka ma h'a yaksha ku be ra /
T02TD3731E:67b-12: yi ge de la bsgrub bya dang //
T02TD3731E:67b-13: gsad pa'i yi ge gdags par bya //
T02TD3731E:67b-14: mchod pa snying gar gdags par bya //
T02TD3731E:67b-15: dug la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams kyis //
T02TD3731E:67b-16: gzugs la legs par byug par bya//
T02TD3731E:67b-17: de yi steng du rdo leb la //
T02TD3731E:67b-18: rdo rje rgya gram bris nas ni //
T02TD3731E:67b-19: lingga'i snying gar gzhug par bya //
T02TD3731E:67b-20: de yi steng du mchod rten ni //
T02TD3731E:67b-21: sngon po khru gang tshad du brtsig / bum par rgyal po chen po yi //
T02TD3731E:67b-22: gsad pa'i sngags ni bris te gzhug / slob dpon chen po 'gro bzang snying pos mdzad pa'i rnam thos sras kyi drag byed kyi cho ga rdzogs so /
T02TD3731E:67b-24: // / rgya gar dbus kyi pandi ta chen po te dza de ba dang /
T02TD3731E:67b-25: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong zangs dkar 'phags pa shes rab kyis bsgyur ba'o//
